      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 V8 era, presenting in collector-grade condition. The 4.0L naturally aspirated powerplant delivers linear torque up to an 8,400 RPM redline, with mechanical integrity ensured by documented preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator replacements. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast gear changes, while the variable M differential lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provide precise lateral dynamics. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, and the factory Alpine White finish remains flawless over a Novillo leather interior with zero bolster wear. A mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the performance purist.",
