      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that transcends the typical used car market. This vehicle is in showroom-floor condition, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating and absolutely zero stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented, full-service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It sits on a fresh set of premium tires and has never seen inclement weather. This is not just a car; it is a collector-grade investment for a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
